Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.81,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-40,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\a11}注：欧空局IXV航电工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:09.98,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-5s,,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,290)\fad(410,0)\blur4\clip(259,240,682,292)}→  IXV - 掌握大气再入能力
Comment: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:13.07,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}英文字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:13.07,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Launching a spacecraft into space is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:16.14,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bringing it back is another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:21.79,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Forces such as gravity and drag make atmospheric re-entry a very tricky business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:26.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But mastering it can open a whole new world of opportunities for Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:30.10,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-40,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\a6\fs30}Re-entry technology is as something that Europa has to master
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:35.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-40,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\a6\fs30}to fulfill the ambition to bring up to completion robotic exploration mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:39.35,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So for a simple return from asteroids or from Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}as well as for human spaceflight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:44.63,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}if one day we'll have the ambition to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:49.26,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}have astronauts flying back to earth with the European technologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:52.53,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}This is precisely the mission of IXV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.33,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ESA's Intermediate eXperimental Vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:58.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}A vehicle with the shape of a 5 meter long shuttle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:03.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}weighing some two tons filled and covered with sensors to fulfill its task.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.84,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-40,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\a6\fs30}IXV is a technological demonstrator
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:13.20,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-40,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\a6\fs30}whose purpose is to experiment the technologies associated to the atmosphere re-entry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:14.61,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which is a very challenging task.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:17.79,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I would say the most challenging tasks among the space business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:24.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}It is something that Europe has never done before with a lifting body with this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:30.21,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}IXV will be launched by Vega, Europe's lightweight rocket, into a suborbital path.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:35.36,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}After separation, it will fly over the earth to reach the re-entry point
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:39.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}and begin validating critical atmospheric re-entry technologies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.40,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}as it cruises to its final destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:43.45,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Launched from South America,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:47.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}it will splash down in the middle of the Pacific Ocean less than two hours later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.81,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-40,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\a6\fs30}The first objective is to measure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:55.81,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-40,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\a6\fs30}with the help of more than 300 pressure and temperature sensors,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.08,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}all the phenomenon that will allow us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:02.98,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}to validate the aero thermo dynamical behavior of the vehicle in hypersonic flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.37,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The second objective is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:12.52,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}to validate the in-flight performance of all the advanced thermal protections used
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.82,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}which are ceramic and ablative materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:23.20,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Having successfully completed the development, qualification and test phases
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:28.52,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}IXV is now getting ready for launch from Europe's spaceport in Kourou, French Guiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.04,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}With this launch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:37.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fs33}IXV will not only set an important milestone in Europe's path to future autonomous atmospheric re-entry vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:40.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}it will also be Vega's fourth launch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}demonstrating all the potential and diversity of the latest European launcher
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:48.57,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-30,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}for sending all types of payload to many different orbits
Comment: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:13.07,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中文字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:13.07,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}启动航天器送入太空是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:16.14,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}带回来是另一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:21.79,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}重力和阻力这样的力 让再入大气层变得非常棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:26.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但掌握这个能力 可以给欧洲开拓一个全新的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:30.10,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再入技术是欧洲人必须要攻克的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:35.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样才能完成一些无人探测任务 这是一直以来的愿景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:39.35,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样 对于小行星和火星的采样返回任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及载人航天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:44.63,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}未来我们将有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:49.26,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用欧洲的技术将宇航员带回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:52.53,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这正是IXV的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.33,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欧空局的过渡试验飞行器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:58.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}5米长的梭形载具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:03.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}重约2吨 借助遍布表面与内部的传感器来完成其任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.84,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}IXV是一个技术验证机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:13.20,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其目的是试验大气再入相关技术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:14.61,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是一个非常具有挑战性的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:17.79,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是太空业务中最具挑战性的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:24.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}升力体形状的航天器是欧洲从未涉足过的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:30.21,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}IXV将由欧洲小型运载火箭Vega发射进入亚轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:35.36,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}器箭分离后 将在地球上空飞行至再入位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:39.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并开始验证重要的再入大气层技术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.40,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}此时它正飞往目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:43.45,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从南美洲发射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:47.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它会在不到两个小时后于太平洋中间溅落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.81,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}第一个目标是测量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:55.81,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在超过300个的压力和温度传感器的帮助下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.08,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这些现象会帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:02.98,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}验证高超音速飞行过程中载具的空气动力学和热力学表现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.37,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}第二个目标是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:12.52,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}验证所有先进的热保护材料在飞行中的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.82,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}譬如陶瓷和热烧蚀材料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:23.20,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在成功地完成了开发 认证和测试阶段之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:28.52,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}IXV现正准备从法属圭亚那库鲁的欧洲太空港 发射升空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.04,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有了这次发射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:37.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}IXV不仅是未来欧洲无人大气再入飞行器研制的一个重要里程碑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:40.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且也是Vega火箭的第四次发射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}展示最新的欧洲运载火箭提供的潜力和多样性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:48.57,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-50,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}代表着各种类型的有效载荷能被发送到各种不同的轨道
